  "observations": [
    "Hierarchical left-panel tree nav: Metalake → Catalog → Schema → Table/Fileset/Topic/Function",
    "Detail view shows entity metadata top + properties table + tabs for children/tags/policies/audit",
    "in-use/not-in-use as prominent toggle switch at entity header, gates child operations",
    "Catalog creation is multi-step wizard: pick type → pick provider → provider-specific dynamic fields",
    "Provider-based dynamic forms: selecting Hive vs MySQL vs Iceberg changes required fields",
    "Tags and policies attached via m2m — multi-select dialog from parent entity detail",
    "Hover popovers on tree nodes show brief metadata preview without navigation",
    "Drop operations gated by type-to-confirm dialog for name match (irreversibility high)",
    "RBAC: Role carries securableObjects[] with granted privileges on hierarchy path",
    "Job templates hold placeholder slots substituted at run_job invocation",
    "Properties modelled as open-ended key-value map, edited inline in detail view",
    "Schema/Table/Fileset/Topic are sibling children of Schema, picked by catalog.type",
    "Audit fields (createdAt/createdBy) shown read-only in detail header"
  ]
